:VitalInterests rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/kyith/ontologies/2025/6/untitled-ontology-33#Personal_Data_Protection_Act,_B.E._2562_(2019)
<http://www.semanticweb.org/kyith/ontologies/2025/6/untitled-ontology-33#Personal_Data_Protection_Act,_B.E._2562_(2019)> rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                                                                                                                                  :PersonalDataProtectionAct ;
                                                                                                                         :has_Chapter :Chapter2 ,
                                                                                                                                      :ChapterI ,
                                                                                                                                      :Introduction ;
                                                                                                                         :definition "Thailand’s Personal Data Protection Act, B.E. 2562 (2019), is the legal framework that governs the processing of personal data in Thailand, establishing rules for data controllers, data processors, and providing rights to data subjects."@en ;
                                                                                                                         :eli:title "Personal Data Protection Act, B.E. 2562 (2019)"@en ;
                                                                                                                         :eli:title_alternative "PDPA Thailand"@en ;
                                                                                                                         rdfs:comment """Personal Data Protection Act, Thailand B.E 2562 (2019)

The PDPA is Thailand's comprehensive personal data protection law, enacted in 2019, that regulates the collection, use, and disclosure of personal data and provides rights to data subjects."""@en ;
                                                                                                                         rdfs:label "PersonalDataProtectionAct_Thailand_BE_2562_2019"@en .


